    "(3.1)Moreover, suppose that(u 1, u 2) ∈ L 2 (0, T; V) × L ∞ (0, T; H).",
    "(3.2)Then the solution (µ, φ, ξ, σ) to (1.1)-(1.5) in the sense of Definition 2.1 enjoys the further regularity propertiesσ ∈ L ∞ (Q), µ ∈ H 1 (0, T; V) ∩ L ∞ (0, T; W), ξ ∈ L ∞ (Q).",
    "(3.3)Proof.",
    "First, observe that condition (3.2) implies (2.17) by Sobolev embeddings.",
